cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper is about the theoretical properties of neural networks with weight matrices of low displacement rank (LDR). The most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper focuses on the universal approximation property and error bounds of LDR neural networks. The second likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as the paper is about neural networks. The third likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as neural networks are commonly used in computer vision. The fourth likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as neural networks are a popular technique in AI. The fifth likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) as neural networks are used in analyzing social networks.
